---
title: "US27 — Browse expert profiles + listings"
---
sequenceDiagram
  actor A as Registered Free User
  participant B as «Boundary»<br/>ExpertsScreen
  participant C as «Control»<br/>LoadExperts
  participant E as «Entity»<br/>ExpertProfile · ExpertService
  A->>B: open Experts tab, search / filter
  B->>C: loadExperts(filter)
  C->>E: listExperts(filter)
  E-->>C: List (ExpertProfile + ExpertService)
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (expert cards)
  B-->>A: directory with ratings + prices
  A->>B: tap Follow on an expert
  B->>C: toggleFollow(expertId)
  C->>E: toggleFollowExpert(expertId)
  E-->>C: follow state
  C-->>B: state = AsyncData (following)
  note over E: planned — listExperts / toggleFollowExpert<br/>via SupabaseGateway (RLS)
